<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:473.34px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">…</span><span class="cls_008">ええ。先週</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">先生が</span><span class="cls_007">  （ </span><span class="cls_008">連れて行ってくださいました</span><span class="cls_007"> ）</span><span class="cls_008">。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:510.54px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">れい</span></div>
